Key Match Events: Giannis Antetokounmpo scored 41 points and had 14 rebounds
Paolo Banchero returned from an injury and scored 34 points
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Bucks moved into a virtual tie with the Magic for fourth place in the East with their third straight win
After going 19-15 in Banchero's 10-week absence, the Magic are still missing Jalen Suggs and Franz and Mo Wagner
Others: Damian Lillard added 29 points for the Bucks
Cole Anthony had 18 points and seven rebounds for Orlando and Tristan da Silva had 16 points and 10 rebounds
Bobby Portis came off Milwaukee's bench to score 11 points and grab seven rebounds
